And then increment it by 1:

    &lt;button mat-raised-button (click)=&quot;addColumn()&quot;&gt; Add column &lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button mat-raised-button (click)=&quot;removeColumn()&quot;&gt; Remove column &lt;/button&gt;
